engineCMS::getHTTP_REFERERServer()

Description
    prviate string engineCMS::getHTTP_REFERERServer(string $referer)

Parameters
    referer
	String value containing the referring server's URL.
	
Return Values
    NULL or valid server URL.

Examples
    
    <?php
	...
	$server = $this->getHTTP_REFERERServer($_SERVER['HTTP_REFERER']);

	if($server != $engineVars['server']) {
	    echo "HTTP Referer check failed.  Possible Cross Site Request Forgery Attack!<br />";
	    exit;
	}
	...
    ?>

